data.description:
OUR PREFERRED LENDER WILL GIVE UP TO $5,000 IN LENDER CREDITS OR A 1-YEAR INTEREST RATE BUYDOWN TO QUALIFIED HOMEBUYERS WITH NO COST REFI. CALL FOR MORE DETAILS

Welcome to your new home! Located in a quiet cul-de-sac in the heart of Parker, CO. This spacious 4-bedroom, 4-bathroom home, fully finished basement and 2 car garage. It is the perfect combination of comfort and convenience. The finished basement adds extra living space, providing versatility and privacy for families or those seeking additional rental income.

Location, location, location!!! This home is close to essential amenities, including top-rated schools, diverse restaurants, and shops. The highly-rated school district enhances the appeal for families looking to settle in a community that values education.

This house offers water softener, drinking water filter, humidifier, air purifier (GPS) all of this is included with the purchase so you can be sure you are coming into a great home with everything you need to make sure your family will be well taken care of. This property has been meticulously maintained and is in excellent shape, making it perfect for large families, first-time homebuyers, or savvy investors seeking rental opportunities. 

Don't miss the chance to make this house your home and be part of a lively community in Parker, CO.
